headline: MoneyMasters Podcast 9-18-25- What's Really Powering the Rally in Stocks and Metals
summary: In this episode of the MoneyShow MoneyMasters Podcast, Sean Brodrick of Weiss Ratings and John Eade of Argus Research unpack today’s market drivers, record equities, gold’s strongest year since 1979, and ongoing Federal Reserve interest rate cuts.
